http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B00010TC30/natilangofthe-20
">Gwich'in Junior Dictionary</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Alaskan Gwich'in language learning book for children.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B007PVPQO2/natilangofthe-20
">Gwich'in Words about the Land</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Bilingual collection of Gwich'in stories and traditional knowledge from the Gwich'in Settlement Region in Canada.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1555000541/natilangofthe-20
">We Traveled from Place to Place</a></b> <IMG SRC="star.gif" ALT="*"> <b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0933769113/natilangofthe-20
">Neets'ąįį Gwiindaii</a>:</b> <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Interesting books of oral history from Venetie and Arctic Village elders, in Western Gwich'in with English translation.
